  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/6a061761a06e5b169ffe1f6044c07dc8.poster.avif?t=1733560418\" width=700 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/6a061761a06e5b169ffe1f6044c07dc8.webm?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/6a061761a06e5b169ffe1f6044c07dc8.mp4?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Dragon Eclipse, you collect magical Mystlings—unique creatures that enhance your deck and join you in battle. Build your team of three Mystlings with distinct stats, abilities, and special cards. Remember that your beasts grow and evolve as you play, so understanding their nature is the key to victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/dbe0dd9df51c45cbfccc15cda918b9d4.poster.avif?t=1733560418\" width=700 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/dbe0dd9df51c45cbfccc15cda918b9d4.webm?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/dbe0dd9df51c45cbfccc15cda918b9d4.mp4?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Combine auto-battler mechanics with deck-building strategy for endless creative possibilities. Unlock new Mystlings, cards, and tougher difficulty levels with every run. Experiment with setups, craft complex combos, and elevate your playstyle to unlock tons of fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/f69342065f1a7624e8b7135f74f6ed5d.poster.avif?t=1733560418\" width=700 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/f69342065f1a7624e8b7135f74f6ed5d.webm?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/f69342065f1a7624e8b7135f74f6ed5d.mp4?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Each Tamer has a distinct playstyle and unique specialization. Which one of them you choose will define the shape of the whole run. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/99a90610041b83b5969c69a463c1cb11.poster.avif?t=1733560418\" width=700 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/99a90610041b83b5969c69a463c1cb11.webm?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/99a90610041b83b5969c69a463c1cb11.mp4?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Every Mystling has unique stats, abilities, and a starting card for your deck. Strategically balance your team, make them your loyal companions, and together, fight against the encroaching evil.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/e98b985ab1d883d475ac861de04b5828.poster.avif?t=1733560418\" width=700 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/e98b985ab1d883d475ac861de04b5828.webm?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/e98b985ab1d883d475ac861de04b5828.mp4?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Mystlings level up and evolve during combat, gaining powerful new abilities. You’ll have to discover and harness their potential. Sweet and unassuming at first, they can transform into fearsome allies under your guidance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/d2bf2213f08cfcdc2f637e402539709a.poster.avif?t=1733560418\" width=700 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/d2bf2213f08cfcdc2f637e402539709a.webm?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/d2bf2213f08cfcdc2f637e402539709a.mp4?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Throughout your journey, you'll construct a powerful deck full of great combos. Acquire new cards from various sources, engage in battles, and encounter intriguing characters to ensure your deck is tailored to your combat preferences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/fa812207b1f83fd4e98c4aebd7b9de77.poster.avif?t=1733560418\" width=700 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/fa812207b1f83fd4e98c4aebd7b9de77.webm?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/fa812207b1f83fd4e98c4aebd7b9de77.mp4?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The approaching Eclipse limits your time to gather resources and cards. Not the whole map can be explored. Make decisions to secure victory before it's too late.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Are you ready to become the ultimate Tamer? Start your journey today!</strong></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/6a061761a06e5b169ffe1f6044c07dc8.poster.avif?t=1733560418\" width=700 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/6a061761a06e5b169ffe1f6044c07dc8.webm?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/6a061761a06e5b169ffe1f6044c07dc8.mp4?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Dragon Eclipse, you collect magical Mystlings—unique creatures that enhance your deck and join you in battle. Build your team of three Mystlings with distinct stats, abilities, and special cards. Remember that your beasts grow and evolve as you play, so understanding their nature is the key to victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/dbe0dd9df51c45cbfccc15cda918b9d4.poster.avif?t=1733560418\" width=700 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/dbe0dd9df51c45cbfccc15cda918b9d4.webm?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/dbe0dd9df51c45cbfccc15cda918b9d4.mp4?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Combine auto-battler mechanics with deck-building strategy for endless creative possibilities. Unlock new Mystlings, cards, and tougher difficulty levels with every run. Experiment with setups, craft complex combos, and elevate your playstyle to unlock tons of fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/f69342065f1a7624e8b7135f74f6ed5d.poster.avif?t=1733560418\" width=700 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/f69342065f1a7624e8b7135f74f6ed5d.webm?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/f69342065f1a7624e8b7135f74f6ed5d.mp4?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Each Tamer has a distinct playstyle and unique specialization. Which one of them you choose will define the shape of the whole run. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/99a90610041b83b5969c69a463c1cb11.poster.avif?t=1733560418\" width=700 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/99a90610041b83b5969c69a463c1cb11.webm?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/99a90610041b83b5969c69a463c1cb11.mp4?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Every Mystling has unique stats, abilities, and a starting card for your deck. Strategically balance your team, make them your loyal companions, and together, fight against the encroaching evil.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/e98b985ab1d883d475ac861de04b5828.poster.avif?t=1733560418\" width=700 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/e98b985ab1d883d475ac861de04b5828.webm?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/e98b985ab1d883d475ac861de04b5828.mp4?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Mystlings level up and evolve during combat, gaining powerful new abilities. You’ll have to discover and harness their potential. Sweet and unassuming at first, they can transform into fearsome allies under your guidance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/d2bf2213f08cfcdc2f637e402539709a.poster.avif?t=1733560418\" width=700 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/d2bf2213f08cfcdc2f637e402539709a.webm?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/d2bf2213f08cfcdc2f637e402539709a.mp4?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Throughout your journey, you'll construct a powerful deck full of great combos. Acquire new cards from various sources, engage in battles, and encounter intriguing characters to ensure your deck is tailored to your combat preferences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/fa812207b1f83fd4e98c4aebd7b9de77.poster.avif?t=1733560418\" width=700 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/fa812207b1f83fd4e98c4aebd7b9de77.webm?t=1733560418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626860/extras/fa812207b